<br>
Chained till i could chain no more <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ujmilster.showPublicProfile?language=EN>jmilster</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#333333>(3/19/01 7:50:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=181.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Post your toughest solo smackdown Mages :)</span><hr size=1> Quag and a regular cyclops in OOT. I actually won using the pet recast strategy. I was 51 when this happened. <br>
<br>
Cyrranin Emrys<br>
